        "label": "Otter API key",
        "generateUrl": "https://otter.ai/setting/developer",
        "setup": "Sign in to your Otter account, open [Developer settings](https://otter.ai/setting/developer) from **Integrations → Developer**, then click **Create key** and copy the key. The Help Center notes this feature is available for Enterprise workspaces; if you do not see it, contact your Otter account manager as described in [Otter.ai Public API](https://help.otter.ai/hc/en-us/articles/36130822688279-Otter-ai-Public-API). Send it as `Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY`.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
